OL,5, Radio presenter Susan Rae has thanked  
OL,6, listeners for their support and "lovely
OL,7, messages" since being diagnosed with   
OL,8, early onset Alzheimer's last year.     
OL,10,FThe sons of the freelance Radio 4      
OL,11,Fannouncer launched an appeal this week 
OL,12,Fto support her move to assisted living 
OL,13,Fand it has raised #40,000 in five days.
OL,15,FRae told Radio 4's Broadcasting House  
OL,16,Fshow she was "overwhelmed" by the      
OL,17,Fsupport people had shown her.          
OL,19,FShe said it was "the most extraordinary
OL,20,Fmoment" since her diagnosis.           
